storage: none

nuget FSharp.Analyzers.SDK 0.36.0

// Vendored fork of FSharpLint. Kept ONLY for a TransparentCompiler `ProjectOptions`
// guard (try/with -> None; upstream Lint.fs is unguarded and throws when check
// results come from FCS's TransparentCompiler — the shim's host, fshw, uses it).
// Upstream master ALREADY has everything else the shim needs: the two-phase
// `lintParsedFile` API (byte-identical) and FCS 43.12. This branch is now synced
// with upstream master (perf/rule fixes pulled in) + our guard + crypto.xml 10.0.10.
// WAITING FOR fsprojects/FSharpLint#872 (Numpsy's project-context wrapper — the
// maintainer's preferred fix over our #862/#863). Once #872 (or #862/#863) lands in
// an upstream nightly, drop this git-dep and switch to upstream FSharpLint.Core.
git https://github.com/michaelglass/FSharpLint.git perf/two-phase-lint-api
